divs: sighting detailswas taking pictures of the sunset after a rainfall. was standing in my front yard. upon examining film, disc shape shows in one photo but not in the previous or next slide taken within the same 60 seconds. 5:30pm on 5\24\10. attached in 2nd photo is a close up. using the street lights as a frame of reference, the object appears quite large. the street lights are located approx 3\4 of a mile from me. it is not the moon or a star as those would have appeared in every photo.
